1) So here we are going to install jenkins by making use of docker image which already have all the jenkins 
    configuration available.
2) so lets go to the below URL Docker imgae URL and follow the below steps in order to pull that image
    https://hub.docker.com/r/jenkins/jenkins/
    Use below command from above web page
    # docker pull jenkins/jenkins
    This docker pull command will pull the docker jenkins image from Docker Hub.
    we can use below command for checking the available pulled image
    # docker images
3) To check the Docker root directory or to check the place where docker is storing all its files we can use below
    command
    # docker info | grep -i root
        Docker Root Dir: /var/lib/docker
    

